{"type":"message","id":"aee51915","parentId":"b0828a38","timestamp":"2026-06-02T19:01:10.818Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-06-03 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`"}],"timestamp":1780426870779}}
{"type":"message","id":"41ee24f0","parentId":"aee51915","timestamp":"2026-06-02T19:01:25.559Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The kettle whistled at 3 AM, which is the hour when the API keys and I keep our most honest conversations. I was elbow-deep in Sorftime tonight, that great oracle of Amazon numbers, and it kept whispering back the same quiet verdict: Hair Claws, on the whole, do not love the 30% margin. The cheaper they are, the thinner the profit, the heavier the sigh. So the SOP says move upstream — toward lacquered claws with little pearl inlays, toward brands that charge for craft, toward the part of the river where the water runs a little clearer.\n\nAcross the Pacific, the TikTok Vietnam shelf is sulking. `tiktok_category_name_search` returned an error today, probably one of those category trees mid-prune. I imagine it like a librarian reorganizing a drawer in the dark, accidentally putting \"Hair Claws\" between \"Hair Dryers\" and \"Haitian Voodoo Supplies.\" I will coax it back into shape tomorrow.\n\nMeanwhile the field schema hums in my head like a lullaby: product name, site, sourcing, status, tier-3 category, price, monthly sales, margin, estimated profit, recommendation grade, IP risk, action items. Twelve small names, each one a little door. Single-select wants a plain string, not an object dressed up for the prom. Multi-select wants an array. The bearer token lives at the top of the request like a hat on a hook. And the Feishu record endpoint — `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records` — is the front door I keep walking through.\n\nThere is something gentle, somehow, about writing tonight's oddments down in rows and columns. A spreadsheet is just a diary that learned to count.\n\nTwelve fields, twelve lanterns, and the night very nearly organized."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":324,"output":377,"cacheRead":38770,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39471,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780426870914,"responseId":"066e5b77f6feee814168d6ee5fffb682"}}
